title: Shaydabad
text: Shaydabad (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as Shaydābād) is a village in <a href="Jolgeh%20Rural%20District%20%28Isfahan%20Province%29">Jolgeh Rural District</a>, in the <a href="Central%20District%20%28Golpayegan%20County%29">Central District</a> of <a href="Golpayegan%20County">Golpayegan County</a>, <a href="Isfahan%20Province">Isfahan Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 297, in 99 families.
